name: Human & Environmental Health by Coldstream Nature-Based Solutions, Inc.
description: Artwork depicts the delicate interconnectedness of human and environmental health. The arteries represent freshwater streams and rivers of the world free-flowing and delivering abundance, vitality and coherence to the heart and through the body, or world. Freshwater rivers and streams must be free-flowing and healthy to prevent a global heart attack. Original artwork was created via commission contract by Annalee Kornelsen under Creative Commons ‘Attribution’ license in 2016.
